“defendant”,  in  relation  to  a  maintenance  order  or  a  related 
attachment  of  earnings  order,  means  the  person  liable  to  make 
payments  under  the  maintenance  order;

and  where  this  Act  are  applicable  by  virtue  of  an  authorization 
under  section  14  to  or  in  respect  of  a  maintenance  order  made 
by  a  Syariah  Court,  includes  such  order;

